# Reflection / Self-Critique — REST Client (VS Code: REST Client by Huachao Mao)
# Run worker: npm run worker:reflection (from repo root)

@base = http://localhost:3000
@workflowId = <paste workflowId from start response>

### Start reflection workflow
POST {{base}}/workflows/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowType": "reflectionWorkflow",
  "input": {
    "topic": "Why reusable packaging matters"
  }
}

### Get run status
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}

### Get run result (wait until status is COMPLETED)
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}/result
